                length="13944010"
                type="application/octet-stream"
            />
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Improvement</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Update app icon and logo assets, refactor AppHeader view to use new logo image</li>
    <li>Implement bit-perfect playback with sample rate synchronization (hog mode)</li>
    <li>Audio device change option within UI</li>
    <li>Implement M3U playlist import and export functionality, and add folder as playlist import feature</li>
    <li>Implement persistent sorting for library views, including albums, artists, genres, and tracks, with saved sort options and fields</li>
    <li>Implement music import progress tracking and UI, with import status display and folder scanning improvements</li>
</ul>
<h2>Fixes</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Enhance full-text search with weighted ranking, BM25 scoring, and improved tokenization ( rebuild FTS going Settings -> Advance)</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/rvarunrathod/HiFidelity/compare/v1.0.5...v1.0.6">Full Changelog</a></p>
